{"tid":1258332,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇可能俾全世界知Facebook點樣協助支共","createTime":"2019-06-26T05:06:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T11:41:41.000Z","uid":165336,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"54e78e635506283229e8751f643cab1394db7b4d","tid":1258332,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T05:06:34.000Z","msg":"仆街FB,d廢老港豬3毛講乜都得<br />\nd5毛講埋d又打又殺既野都唔刪唔封<br />\n但我就因為同佢地開片俾人凍結左好多次<br />\n就算冇用&quot;支那&quot;都有機會凍結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到而家屌人都要就住就住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nd仆街貼假新聞又唔撚刪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然大部份廢老都係靠wechat互傳<br />\n但無可否認FB仍然係有一定影響力<br />\n仲有好多唔知係咪建制派人士開既偽中立group<br />\n表面上就唔刪post自由討論<br />\n實際上就充斥大量3毛,on9言論同假新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n莫名其妙地好撚多人入<br />\n甚至有馬東西亞人係度問香港情況<br />\n然後又一堆5毛係度講埋d乜撚野西方國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如呢d<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/295202647488775/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F295202647488775%2F&d=BBPgAQHQe62%2Fb%2Fw120tVmR5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=f95fc693\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/295202647488775/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/1908584002693059/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F1908584002693059%2F&d=BBPgAQHQe62%2Fb%2Fw120tVmR5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=498ee331\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/1908584002693059/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/1094495067293073/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F1094495067293073%2F&d=BBPgAQHQe62%2Fb%2Fw120tVmR5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=d129af29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/1094495067293073/</a><br />\n其實開呢d谷既目的係咩野?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有d擺明同高登連登都冇關係既又用高登用語做名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28d4a13721f95e83b96dc488e2a24024b9dda170","tid":1258332,"uid":153722,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T05:10:15.000Z","msg":"你講依堆野好亂 我睇得好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇完 唔覺得Fb有協助中共<br />\n係你fb面對住既三毛五毛 人多+識用fb functions 玩你"},{"pid":"551040e7321a92d8ae41485839e31fedfc555716","tid":1258332,"uid":135040,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T05:20:33.000Z","msg":"以前同五毛罵戰過，搞到用咗7-8年既account 俾人封咗<br />\n而加咩都唔update，冇相冇status，搞到成日俾人話我假account <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4612032134f0498193d1a6d053d8bb5484e91ab9","tid":1258332,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"28d4a13721f95e83b96dc488e2a24024b9dda170","tid":1258332,"uid":153722,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T05:10:15.000Z","msg":"你講依堆野好亂 我睇得好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇完 唔覺得Fb有協助中共<br />\n係你fb面對住既三毛五毛 人多+識用fb functions 玩你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T05:21:45.000Z","msg":"Facebook停止翻譯所有示威相關嘅內容<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1236758\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1236758</a><br />\n<br />\n有無人個facebook 怪怪地，show少左好多野<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href